| Both photos + Feishu link               | Read table first вҶ’ merge with photo extraction вҶ’ ask user to resolve conflicts |

**If reading from Feishu table:**
Load `references/feishu-api.md` вҶ’ Step 1 (get token) + Step 2 (read all records).
Parse each record's fields into the structured format below.

**If extracting from photos:**
For each vaccine entry, capture:

- Vaccine name вҶ’ **`з–«иӢ—еҗҚз§°` column** = canonical name **only** (no гҖҢз¬¬XеүӮгҖҚin that cell); dose goes in **`еүӮж¬Ў`**. Booklet wording may still be parsed as separate fields.
- Dose number вҶ’ **`еүӮж¬Ў`** (з¬¬еҮ й’Ҳ/з¬¬еҮ еүӮ)
- Date administered (жҺҘз§Қж—Ҙжңҹ) вҖ” YYYY-MM-DD
